title: V05 — Containers & Supporters
story: familyzoo
author: Sharpee Tutorial
description: Verify containers (backpack, dispenser) and supporters (bench)

---

# V5 teaches: ContainerTrait, SupporterTrait, put in, put on

# Take the backpack (portable container)
> take backpack
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Take the map
> take map
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Put map inside backpack
> put map in backpack
[OK: contains "put"]

# Look inside backpack to see contents
> look in backpack
[OK: contains "zoo map"]

# Go to Main Path for the supporter test
> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]

# Take the penny
> take penny
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Put penny on the park bench (supporter)
> put penny on bench
[OK: contains "put"]

# The bench should show the penny
> examine bench
[OK: contains "park bench"]

# Go to Petting Zoo for the scenery container
> east
[OK: contains "Petting Zoo"]

# The dispenser is a scenery container — can't take it
> take dispenser
[OK: contains "fixed in place"]

# But we can examine it
> examine dispenser
[OK: contains "feed dispenser"]
[OK: contains "FREE"]
